  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, VRehab aims to deliver rehabilitation programs virtually to patients' homes and has the potential to overcome many barriers to program attendance and completion 28, 29.",
    "Integrating AI into VRehab to automate different stages of rehabilitation holds significant potential for complementing clinicians and improving the quality of care they provide to patients in their homes.",
    "AI-driven VRehab platforms offer promising solutions for addressing the shortage of rehabilitation staff and optimizing operational efficiencies.",
    "By delivering rehabilitation services virtually to patients' homes, VRehab expands access to healthcare for diverse populations, including those who are underrepresented and reside in remote communities without access to rehabilitation centers 2, 3, 5, 7.",
    "However, for VRehab to be effective, patients need access to computers or smart devices, sensors, and an internet connection at home."
